text: Jangsak is a settlement located on the western outskirts of Bandar Seri Begawan, the capital of Brunei. Officially known in Malay as (sometimes ), It is a village-level subdivision under Kilanas, a mukim of Brunei-Muara District. The postcode for Jangsak is BF2720. == References == Category:Populated places in Brunei Category:Villages of Brunei
title: Jangsak
